  <issue_management
    owner="Rob Bodington"
    priority="low"
    category="properties"/>
<description>
 <p>
   <b>SC4 part number:</b>  </p>
 <p>
   <b>(2) Clause:</b> ARM Express
 </p>
 <p>
   <b>(3) Paragraph:</b> Assigned_property.described_element
 </p>
 <p>
   <b>(5) Comment:</b>
 </p>
 <p>
Currently Assigned_property can not be reused. If a type of property and a specific value apply to more than one instance of product data (property_assignment_select), both Assigned_property and Property_representation need to be instantiated repeatedly. This leads to an undesired and unnecessary proliferation of data.</p>
 <p>
   <b>(6) Proposal:</b>
 </p>
 <p>
Make Assigned_property.described_element an aggregate or at least Property_representation.property.</p>
 </description>

<comment
   by="Nigel Shaw" 
   date="04-10-07">
   <description>
	   Agreed with NO representative that proposal does not allow tracking of history of properties over time and is therefore rejected.
</description>
</comment>

